Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-60,0:00:-03.-02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-03.00,0:00:00.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-16,0:00:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an exit... It's an entrance!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heso!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm coming to a stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who crashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure does require you to get the hang of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!! You're the coolest!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This is incredible! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she able to ride that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where did Nami-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, I wonder if she's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Conis-san, I'm a bit concerned myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here in Skypiea, there's a place that we're\Nnever to step foot in no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never to step foot in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's sacred ground.\N--Sacred ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We call that place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Upper Yard, the land where God lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Forbidden Sacred Ground! The Island\NWhere God Lives and Heaven's Judgment!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a place where we're never to set foot in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes.\N--God... you mean that God?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God lives on the sky island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Since Skypiea is God's Land,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's ruled by the Almighty God Eneru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Almighty God?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Eneru knows everything in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also watching us all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All the time?!\N--Now, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He's watching us now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. God, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe in God?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Whether or not\NGod exists doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't care less from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't intend to deny\Nthose who want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, have you seen that God who\Nlives in Upper Yard, Conis-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! God forbid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot step foot in Upper Yard. Never...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sacred ground, Upper Yard, is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the sky island has ground, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:05:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. A place that we're not\Nallowed to go no matter what, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Your eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you thinking about right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen good! "Never step foot in" means
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're absolutely not\Nsupposed to go there, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see... So there's a place\Nthat we're not supposed to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. A place that we're absolutely\Nnot supposed to go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely planning to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? But if he's God, wouldn't he forgive you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you go someplace you're\Nnot supposed to? He's nice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... But breaking God's\Nrules is blasphemous, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well, I guess it doesn't matter either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because he intends to go\Neven if he won't be forgiven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happens if someone goes\Ninto that forbidden Upper Yard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person cannot come back alive.\NEveryone believes so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cannot come back alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm worried about Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she isn't near Upper Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami-san!! Stay where you are\N--In any case, let's go there, to find Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--and don't go anywhere!!\N--Is your reason for going really to find Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami-san!!\N--Isn't it really so you can\Ngo to the forbidden land?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the huge trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen something this big before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are these trees?\NSeveral hundred years?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All these trees...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see the top of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The treasure should definitely be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:07:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An extraordinary treasure is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're very close, it's almost within our grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The treasure is close by! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice came from over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... Hold on a second.\NWe'll go after I finish these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do if\Nsomething happens to Nami-san
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while you're sitting around like it's nothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave them there,\Nsince we're coming right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... Hold on! This one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis-chan, it'll be night if I wait for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to that Upper Yard place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we don't know if she was really headed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if we incur God Eneru's wrath,\Nwe'll really be in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Eneru seems to be pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:08:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Eneru... God, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...seems to be on that boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claw marks...! I wonder if it\Nwas attacked by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The treasure should definitely be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An extraordinary treasure is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're very close...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Th-The seashell is talking!\N--It's almost within our grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Th-The seashell is talking!\N--The treasure is close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a seashell, right? There's no\Nway there's a human in here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:09:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! If we keep a record like this,\Nit may become useful later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this seashell can record voices!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't want to! I'm going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm scared! I can feel it!\NI can feel God's anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that noise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By God?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back. It's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems better to leave this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we're off!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the place we're not allowed to go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I'm sorry! There's a headwind right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this wind, going to Upper Yard\Nwill take quite long! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Quite long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this ship moved using dial energy,\Nit wouldn't take that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you mean by "quite long"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Only the wind knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I see... Quite long, huh?\N--Old guy! Isn't there any other way
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'd very much like to go,\Nsince I'm worried about Nami.\N--Old guy! Isn't there any other way
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'd very much like to go,\Nsince I'm worried about Nami.\N--to get there quicker?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Even I, Usopp-sama, the hero...\N--to get there quicker?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Even I, Usopp-sama, the hero...\N--We'd better hurry, or Nami will be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't control the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! So that was why, after all!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--"That"? Which "that"?\N--You liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! That son of a bitch! He took my prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? I can hear noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should, too. He's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoho! Same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoho!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What on earth...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on... in this forest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's finally a dangerous place we can go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sit around and wait\Ntill the wind changes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Luffy! Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the old broken waver?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:13:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was obviously going to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do? He sank again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're such a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is your old waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found it in the sea in the world below.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like me to take a look?\NIf it can be fixed, I'll fix it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fix it, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dial ship engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Then, please fix it! Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you want to compete, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind fighting with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to kill my boredom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! That's a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to put your\Nbody in this guy's stomach?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hohoho! Small fries crushing each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be a sight! Hoho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the small fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ride with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... Ride with me? But this\Nis a one-person boat, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here from another sky\Nisland in search of treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't care about it any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can another person ride on this? I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even if I had to kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guerrilla!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:16:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-God...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a bitch! Is this Eneru's doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you harm Vearth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get some Water Dials now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:19.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Angel Island Lovely Street"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together now, salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heso!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Captain McKinley\NWhite Berets, Skypiea Police"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heso, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the White Berets!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illegal entrants have infiltrated\NSkypiea through Angel Beach today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was reported that there are\Na total of seven infiltrators!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the White Berets,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are currently conducting a\Nfull-scale search for these criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch out for suspicious individuals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:18:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like that man\Nwas talking to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a guerrilla. He's just run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shut that dog up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was probably begging for his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is Eneru-sama thinking,\Ntaking care of that man by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were we...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We probably ran out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran out of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another group of illegal entrants\Nhas already infiltrated this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady Amazon informed us that it's a\Nship with seven Blue Sea people on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven Blue Sea people... Could he mean us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said illegal entrants...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to the upper area,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pay the entrance fee of\None billion Extol per person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be because we\Ndidn't pay the entrance fee?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who were riding that boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and, that man, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they entered illegally, they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, will the same thing that\Nhappened to that man happen to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no challenge in taking\Ncare of only seven people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven heads... We can't divide them by four.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell everyone immediately!\NThis place is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Usopp, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine's finished, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check out that art!\NDon't they look just like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how does that look like us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I think... of your art!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--While Nami-san could be in danger,\Nyou're fooling around!!\N--Stop it! How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take this! And this!\N--Stop it! How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take this! And this!\N--Don't take it out on my art!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Can it be fixed?\N--I've never seen these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please fix it one way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I can't say much\Nuntil I investigate it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, please try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try disassembling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old guy, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, suspicious ship over there, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:21:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck are they crawling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably... weirdos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! So those are weirdos...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Heso!\N--Heso!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, heso!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what're you guys saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp said they're weirdos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the seven illegal entrants\Nwho came from the Blue Sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll humbly bring Heaven's Judgment upon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! That's still only a 5th degree crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good! When it's determined\Nto be a 5th degree crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the name of God Eneru,\Nyou'll be banished to the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banished to the clouds?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Being banished to\Nthe clouds sounds kinda nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't! It's the death penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death penalty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.73,0:23:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Already Criminals?!\NSkypiea's Upholders of the Law"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.73,0:23:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
